Azure LB:


     Lb creation can be created with availablity sets   
     Backend pools should be from same avail.set
     Vm's security group should allow ports to any port 
     Loadbalancer ip is static...
     Private subnet creation  - Name your subnet private
     NAT rule for using as jump server to another private server 
     Inbound traffic rule for Http internet facing loadbalancer 
     Probe health first , then Traffic rule


Azure storage:
    
     Create storage account and add file(or) blob (or) queue 
     Generate sas key for storage account 
     az login
     az storage 


Az keys and connection string




